::DarkMouse::

She shivered.  She whispered,"I'm cold." The drug that Black Aracnia 
gave her hadn't fully worn off yet.  She shivered and looked around. 
"Where am I?" she whispered.  She looked and saw the lab.  But where 
the lab was or who it belonged to she wasn't sure.  She still felt a 
litle groggy.  She kept looking around the room, but with her eyes 
only.  She couldn't really move her head yet.  Her body just shook 
and didn't want to respond to her thoughts.  She whispered 
again,"Where an I? I"m cold" she closed her eyes hoping the shivering 
and shaking would stop soon.
